snippet.textDisplay: The concept is a clear rip off from Haule Haule by Rab Ne Bana Di Jodi, but I would rather watch this everyday than the former. The song is awesome and vibrant. Thumbs Up to Coke Studio Pakistan for always being innovative with their music and concepts.
